src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自膠左先<br />\n都唔得你有冇多條pcie吉下睇下有冇反應<br />\n極端d就蚊晒所有線usb sata果d 得番u 卡 ram<br />\n開機睇下有冇畫面<br />\n都唔得搵多部電腦試下張卡就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdcb0245d95f2f1eb425b9d1ade09b1b1f02beac","tid":47742,"uid":707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"Btw你塊板咩型號"},{"pid":"ff0a061d5e5d50d88fe13cf29a6ffe4e7457c18d","tid":47742,"uid":68186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用舊既就ok ,但換張新既係點解會no signal，<br />\n狀況1:平時開機有b一聲 ，換左張新卡就沒 ，代表張卡壞 正常唔到開機？<br />\n<br />\n狀況2:有電既個風扇轉緊，應該唔關沒電事<br />\n<br />\n有沒巴打解答一下 ，感激🙏🏻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有機底板太舊搵唔到張卡 更新下bois睇下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBios<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  自膠左先<br />\n都唔得你有冇多條pcie吉下睇下有冇反應<br />\n極端d就蚊晒所有線usb sata果d 得番u 卡 ram<br />\n開機睇下有冇畫面<br />\n都唔得搵多部電腦試下張卡就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我都唔太熟電腦結構既野 <br />\nPcie係display card 槽？如果係得一個 試唔到⋯<br />\n但想問一下 我插display 個位置有沒問題 我係個mon 連住左display card dvi 個位，hdmi 同vga 洗唔洗試埋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/151555_fea16b9fc8387f8ed1205df0fff69c87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F151555_fea16b9fc8387f8ed1205df0fff69c87.jpg&h=305f75f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條線沒問題 因為舊卡用到 只係唔清楚呢張卡係咪插呢個位<br />\n<br />\n另外係咪要uninstall之前張display card先可以用新既？因為google過下好似可能會有呢個原因"},{"pid":"64ede8edff9977698cb252a6cf67fa873681d1fc","tid":47742,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T07:31:51.000Z","msg":"你個張咩卡黎先"},{"pid":"5139a36c4431d2a1685b60c8c388f81dbc40c4d0","tid":47742,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T09:00:23.000Z","msg":"有冇清乾淨舊driver?<br />\n個陣我淨係換Mon 都搞